Code Example:

# Apply Hadamard and modal transformations alternately
circuit.h(0)
apply_modal_transformation(circuit, angle, 0)
circuit.h(0)  # Return to original state
4. Encoding Modal States
Hadamard gates can be used to encode modal points probabilistically. For instance:

