Over a kkk-dimensional manifold MMM, the integral of HmtH_{mt}Hmt​ takes the form:

∫MHmt∧ϕ,\int_M H_{mt} \wedge \phi,∫M​Hmt​∧ϕ,

where ϕ\phiϕ is a test form, and ∧\wedge∧ is the wedge product.

