Imt=∫H1→H2Hmt(ψ,ω,m),\mathcal{I}_{mt} = \int_{H_1 \to H_2} H_{mt}(\psi, \omega, m),Imt​=∫H1​→H2​​Hmt​(ψ,ω,m),

